    "After having determined such distributions for the whole range of opinions, we assigned to our simulated agent the distributions associated to their initial opinions.",
    "Figure 6: Estimated probability for a user, in the ideological neighborhood of Emmanuel Macron (center) or Marine Le Pen (far right), to retweet a read message according to the difference of opinion with its author, ∆ op = o reader -o sender, considering periodic boundary conditions.",
